thread.title_full: 3 children, man found in suspicious Hubbard-area fire died of gunshots; woman died of blunt force trauma

author: Jim Ryan | The Oregonian/OregonLive
title: 3 children, man found in suspicious Hubbard-area fire died of gunshots; woman died of blunt force trauma
text: Deputies didn't publicly identify the decedents, but the bodies appear to be a family of five that lived in the Hubbard-area home: Erin and Keith Kroeker, ages 39 and 42, and their three school-age children -- 10-year-old twin boys and a 7-year-old girl.
